  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">The number of penguins in a zoo exhibit, sorted by gender and type of penguin, is shown in the table above. Which type of penguin has a female population that is the closest to being <span class=\"math_expression \"><span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"one-third \"></span></span> of the total <span class=\"underline\"><span class=\"formatted_text text_decoration:underline \">female</span></span> penguin population in the exhibit?</p>\n",
  "answerOptions": [
    {
      "id": "a",
      "content": "<p>Chinstrap</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "id": "b",
      "content": "<p>Emperor</p>\n"
